    * etc. (ProblemPremise -> Premise)
    * limit to 80 columns wide
    * consistent presentation of __Examples__
    * wtf with haddock on data ƮSection section
    * [] → Set where appropriate
    * enforce unique names
    * clean any messy code
    * check all TODOs
    * implement Variables
    * remove any unused build-depends from cabal

TODO for 0.4.0.0:
